I WILL! rate this when it is finished downloading! Keep checking back. As always you can trust my ratings unlike some people on here which is why I created this account. 

I will rate as a cam and as a whole both out of 10 and also provide feedback and details about the quality.

As a Cam - 7/10
In general quality - 5/10

Have not watch the movie to rate it as a film yet I skimmed through bit by bit and watched the first 5 minutes. 

It doesn't look all that different from the previous uploads except for the fact that its a little brighter but not much. It is the full movie. I would have rated it more but like I said it is dark. Thankfully, the film doesn't have much if any dark or night scenes though. However it is a little blurry, just a small glaze but at some parts it gets even more blurry. The sound is good for a cam as long as your not looking for Surround Sound or anything. This movie is watchable if your not picky, I'm sure there will be a better version out soon if you want to wait though. 

For the complainers about my ratings - I know it is only a cam and its free and believe me, I am thankful for the uploads, but some people want to know the quality before they download it and decide for themselves weather or not they want to wait or watch now. 

Hope I helped! :)
